  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc7\u0bb5\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0b92\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bb4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0bae\u0bb2\u0bc7\u0bb7\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe \u0ba4\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Malaysia ready to extend necessary cooperation to Sri Lanka",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "A meeting between Minister of Justice, Prisons Operations and Constitutional Reforms Wijetasa Rajapaksa and Malaysian High Commissioner to Sri Lanka Tan Young Thai was held at the Ministry of Justice on Wednesday 29th.",
        "The meeting focused on market and diplomatic relations between the two countries and on further strengthening bilateral relations between Sri Lanka and Malaysia.",
        "The Minister said that the two countries have a long history of friendship and the co-operation of the Government of Malaysia is essential for Sri Lanka to recover from the current economic crisis.",
        "According to a statement issued by the Ministry of Justice, the High Commissioner assured that steps would be taken in the future to further enhance economic and political ties between the two countries and that Sri Lanka would extend its cooperation to Sri Lanka in all necessary cases."
      ],
